==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: monomer
<hw>mon"o*mer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>The basic conceptual building unit of a polymer; a molecule of low
molecular weight which may combine with other molecules to form a
molecule in a chain or branched form having high molecular weight;
<as>as, amino acids are the <ex>monomer</ex> units which are combined to
form proteins; vinylic plastics are formed from <ex>monomers</ex> having
a vinyl group</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>monomeric</ent>⟦br⟧
